om gate\nvoltage. Thus, our work demonstrates feasibility of the macroscopically\ninhomogeneous two-dimensional system as a tunable platform for novel physics\nand proposes the approach for the theoretical description of such systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jul 2018 23:23:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Oct 2019 18:46:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-04"}
